      "comment": "ZIEGFELD (1) is a newcomer to the Seaton Grima yard from Victoria. Hasn't raced for seven weeks but two of his three career wins have come at this distance and he is well served by the ace draw. LOOKIN GOOD MARGIE (2) has been coming from the back row of late, placing at this circuit and distance two back before she was held up and finished midfield last time. Should enjoy better favours from this more favourable draw. EYEKNOW (5) didn't do a bad job when fourth from the back row last time out and placed the last time she raced at this venue. ED MENDES (8) worked last time but was going well prior with a win and two placings from the previous four starts so could be worth another chance.",
